{"tid":438152,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Minecraft 24小時休閒純生存伺服器 正版有白名","createTime":"2017-10-16T15:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T18:31:58.000Z","uid":21749,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"790b5b0c977b26714465fe899acc5aac4348cb79","tid":438152,"uid":21749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"正版限定 純生存 版本: 1.12.2 有白名單 (會keep update最新版本)<br />\n<br />\nServer Setting :<br />\n接近最基本既玩法, PvP disable, 得本牌鎖箱同紅石保護插件, 無指令用<br />\n(領地睇情況再決定裝唔裝...)<br />\n<br />\n規則:<br />\n輕鬆開心玩. 盡量唔好亂搞人, 唔比玩Lag機野, 多謝合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主要招募對象: <br />\n對Minecraft有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 鐘意休閒, 輕鬆, 平淡生活既玩家<br />\n<br />\n加入方法:<br />\n可以係Post度留Game名 或者 入Discord留Game名都得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">Discord:</span> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/t9yDcvG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2Ft9yDcvG&d=Uv8CczrRkfOF72xqJBGoNzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=c84b34ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/t9yDcvG</a><br />\n<br />\nIP: kinglam.mcph.eu<br />\n<br />\n如果有疑問可以係度留言或者去Discord度問都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d62bff15951b94f81a6d6d65974803925886644","tid":438152,"uid":71765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"Watermelon5013<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ec253581f5fef33e4ead5ee2a8c90d838ccbc8","tid":438152,"uid":21749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:52:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Watermelon5013<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nADDED<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b1f207541d939a3926f119b74c99fac28a58ab","tid":438152,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite